GENERAL INFORMATION
ALL FARES one-way plus tax.
RESERVATIONS may be made in ad-
vance and are tentative until tickets are
purchased. Reservations may be cancelled
if passengers fail to check in at Ticket
Counter at least 10 minutes before flight
time.
CHILDREN under 2 years of age, when
carried on lap of adult passenger, travel
free; between 2 years and 12 years at 50
percent rate. Children under 5 years must
be accompanied by a passenger 12 years of
age or over. Minimum fare: $6.00.
MILITARY PERSONNEL, in uniform,
on furlough or leave, may travel on a space
available basis at 50 percent of regular
fare; or on a reserved basis at 75 percent
of regular fare. Minimum fare: $6.00.
CHARTER AIRCRAFT for Service
Clubs, Schools (Flying Geography Tours),
Industry, Sports Groups, Business ... call
your local AERO COMMUTER Station
Manager.
SCHEDULES AND FARES subject to
change without notice.
